   author = {Larisa G Tereshchenko and Nona Sotoodehnia and Colleen M Sitlani and Foram N Ashar and Muammar Kabir and Mary L Biggs and Michael P Morley and Jonathan W Waks and Elsayed Z Soliman and Alfred E Buxton and Tor Biering-Sørensen and Scott D Solomon and Wendy S Post and Thomas P Cappola and David S Siscovick and Dan E Arking},
